{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"59bcc84902","title":"诗一首：给同学","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第一集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cbca6e828d","index":0,"year":1956,"month":11,"day":29,"articleId":"59bcc84902"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0d6384de3f","name":"李冶"},{"id":"fa51fe5561","name":"西南美术专科学校"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7cd00ee52c","type":"title","text":"诗一首：给同学","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"c6ee9246af","type":"authors","text":"西南美术专科学校李冶","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"dd7477bc0a","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：李冶，男，西南美术专科学校附中教员，解放前当过伪军，伪警察，加入过三青团。现为青年团员。这首诗的中心精神是煽动青年学生起来反对党的领导。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"755df2f467","type":"paragraph","text":"在黄桷坪僻远的一角，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"33846455ee","type":"paragraph","text":"人们都沉睡着，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"6277ca3d50","type":"paragraph","text":"除了懒散和懈怠以外，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"a3147678d7","type":"paragraph","text":"压郁了一切蓬勃的","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"6e9cb7f24f","type":"paragraph","text":"生机力量，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"48b0511e56","type":"paragraph","text":"这里的戈尔洛夫们正象","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"9523139e3f","type":"paragraph","text":"一条母猪在糟坑酣睡，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"bb2fb27122","type":"paragraph","text":"舒展着懒腰。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"8198f13098","type":"appellation","text":"*　　*　　*","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"2d68accc38","type":"paragraph","text":"年青的人们，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"6259105ca8","type":"paragraph","text":"你们应该起来呀，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"8d4e9004f7","type":"paragraph","text":"吹起你们的战斗号角，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"6d871aa0b7","type":"paragraph","text":"迈跨你们的雄健步伐，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"2f16c6f8a2","type":"paragraph","text":"昂起首，挺起胸，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"0eb7f73560","type":"paragraph","text":"一点不犹豫，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"aafbaf484c","type":"paragraph","text":"一点不动摇。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"6067270f64","type":"paragraph","text":"勇往直前地","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"a124d96bd1","type":"paragraph","text":"参加战斗吧！","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"8202da937b","type":"appellation","text":"*　　*　　*","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"efd241337b","type":"paragraph","text":"咦，你们怎么不来，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"63ff75b47d","type":"paragraph","text":"难道也睡迷了吗？","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"b704eeecae","type":"paragraph","text":"喔，你们有顾虑，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"84f9bc27c8","type":"paragraph","text":"担忧你们的力量单薄，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"5760989415","type":"paragraph","text":"火力不足，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"0d62569136","type":"paragraph","text":"不，朋友，你们错啦，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"d798210c8d","type":"paragraph","text":"火在地下，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"9591c0d7bf","type":"paragraph","text":"火在四周，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"7a2765c8d8","type":"paragraph","text":"火在人们心中","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"804f863aba","type":"paragraph","text":"只要把它点燃，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"8acb456b87","type":"paragraph","text":"火，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"6842b527fb","type":"paragraph","text":"就会熊熊地燃烧起来，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"2594c53b89","type":"paragraph","text":"赤热地滚动起来，","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"0c2b95e1b9","type":"paragraph","text":"汇合成火的海洋，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"6576df1eb0","type":"paragraph","text":"烧毁腐朽，","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"1fedf872f9","type":"paragraph","text":"烧毁僵躯！","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"},{"id":"4785a028c1","type":"paragraph","text":" 1956．11．29","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902"}],"page":{"id":"b8cf1eb40c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"59bcc84902","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}